      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just mean, it's not even about being \"tired.\" it's like, if i disappeared tomorrow, no one in this city would even notice. my family is thousands of miles away and my coworkers barely know my name. it feels more like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me. does that even make sense?",
